          "reviewBody": "One of the best school... I was there from the mid of 2019 to 2021....\nFirst day was tough to be in that school as i was full of nervousness but the classmates were damn awesome they never let me realise that i was new to them.... ( Ravi, karthik , sumit, sukhman ,kashvi,ritika, tushar , tanushree and manymore) thank you guyz..\nteachers were skilled and so frndly to the students.. the way they teach us they never let us feel  that we were in classroom....\nall teachers were awesome\nbut few names i would like to mention\nVeena Phillips ma'am\nSarika Shinde ma'am\nNeetu Mathew ma'am\nGhazala Musavi ma'am\nRinky ma'am\nVinay sir\nAshutosh sir\nno words remaining... just missing those days..",
